text: Survivor Series (2009) was a professional wrestling pay-per-view (PPV) show made by World Wrestling Entertainment (WWE). It took place on November 22, 2009 at the Verizon Center in Washington, D.C.. It was the 23rd Survivor Series event held by WWE. ==Matches== No. Results Stipulations Times 1 Santino Marella defeated Chavo Guerrero Singles match N/A 2 Team Miz (The Miz, Drew McIntyre, Sheamus,
